video.title: What's CS 124 Honors?
video.msg: JOIN THE DISCORD: https://discord.gg/XBzJRKph3q. Sign up for the class. Non James Scholars: Sign up for the class on self-service (CS199-124). James Scholars: Fill out the HCLA agreement for CS 124. Everyone: Fill out this Google Form to confirm your enrollment https://forms.gle/nLkTxe4nFgkHfa2M8. Enroll in the course on PrairieLearn. CS 124H: Freshman Honors: Introduction to Computer Science I. https://www.prairielearn.org/pl. Add the course calendar: https://calendar.google.com/calendar/...
